From: Claude Sandbox <claude@sandbox.local>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 16:26:43 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Phase 2.1: navigation logo, search overlay,
 FAQ/News/Philosophy pages, footer alignment, new horse silhouette

- Navbar 'Casa Chevalier' brand now links back to /home
- Search icon opens a full-screen search overlay that filters the product catalog
- Split /contacts (contact details + form) from /faq (split-layout accordion)
- New /news editorial article grid page
- New /philosophy page with alternating image/text sections
- Footer: Get in Touch + Company now sit right next to Subscribe (left-aligned)
- Footer links wired to /contacts, /faq, /philosophy, /news
- DropdownMenu 'OUR PHILOSOPHY' -> /philosophy, 'CC NEWS' -> /news
- HorseTransition: redrawn mid-jump silhouette in brand orange with drop shadow
